  "id": "RAW_97e6e177",
  "title": "3 个让我 2025 年效能翻 10 倍的 AI 工具",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTEwNjI2MA==&mid=2651922948&idx=2&sn=5da8b423870cb1943acf4bfddf8b9872",
  "date": "2025-12-25 23:45:00",
  "author": "人人都是产品经理",
  "siteName": "人人都是产品经理",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">上周末在<a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5OTEwNjI2MA==&amp;mid=2651922799&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=5914a3731dc9cd3dc44e44749683f51f&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"2025 AI产品大会现场报道：成本降90%，效率翻倍？大厂专家告诉你，AI如何重塑工作流\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\">&nbsp;AI 产品大会</a>分享了我的一部分 AI 工具和日常，很多小伙伴非常感兴趣要详细清单。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006824\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5625\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"960\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7aae3db2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJsAfL42hTugDqibBm0IaXhXSJYPQN4skSVrPyico6PuW6S1ArZWVc9icNw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D0\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这篇文章整理三个我最高频在用的工具，希望也能帮助大家把日常工作的效率提升起来。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><strong style=\"font-size:inherit;\"><span style=\"visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:inherit;line-height:2;min-height:20px;font-family:inherit;text-align:left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjtnevp-8zcb8y\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 209, 0);font-size:18px;\">#01</span></a></span></strong></span><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最高频&amp;最具性价比：RayCast</span></span></strong></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我今年弃定了&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">ChatGPT</span><span leaf=\"\">、Claude 等所有“原厂”AI，全面拥抱了 RayCast Pro+，月费 $16 可以不限量使用所有模型。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">不止能第一时间用到最新的模型，像 Nano Banana Pro 这种图像模型甚至都没有数量限制。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我今年一共使用了 722 次 RayCast AI，发送了 1097 次消息（这还不包含快捷唤醒的日常提问）</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006827\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6592592592592592\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=384bb78b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJl9R2jibnA3r9UNtdaReXCXDKEAGATfibe11dXghIIM6MkrtJV4DYqAiag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D1\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于 RayCast 提效的功能有很多文章介绍，这里我就不赘述了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">重点分享它的&nbsp;</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">@Ask X</span></code><span leaf=\"\">功能。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006825\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.648854961832061\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"786\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=54940bd4&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJPndaFFqKBNZLnBWMts9Wwtb2Rfpicz0BDF1D4kWYJpPgibSUCNAgsUkw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D2\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">这些</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ask X</span></code><span leaf=\"\">本质上是一些封装的上下文或工具，除了我自己开发的一些&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\">MCP</span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;外，最常用的就是</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ask Clipboard</span></code><span leaf=\"\">和</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Ask Google Chrome</span></code><span leaf=\"\">，前者是把你剪切板里复制的内容直接写入上下文，后者是把浏览器的各项信息写入上下文。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: var(--md-font-family);font-size: var(--md-font-size);line-height: 1.75;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;line-height: 2;font-family: inherit;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;code&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\">Ask Google Chrome</span></span></code><span leaf=\"\">我最喜欢的能力是找我自己看过的网页。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我会直接问“我之前看过一篇关于 Manus 上下文工程的文章，帮我找出来”，它会搜索我的 Chrome 历史记录，找到链接告诉我，同时自己读一遍为我提供总结。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006828\" alt=\"ask_chrome\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img __bg_gif\" data-ratio=\"0.5458758109360519\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"1079\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6c701a00&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJgBjIY6gKNITZiatdJ2zJwficnq0ZxauPTdvRF86ibjyI4lRw9lTOM2ic6A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D3\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\">\n      <span leaf=\"\">ask_chrome</span>\n     </figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">其他还有很多，这篇文章就先不展开了。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">大家可以加入 AI 学习行动圈，后面我出一篇关于 RayCast 的教程。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><strong style=\"font-size:inherit;\"><span style=\"visibility:visible;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:inherit;line-height:2;min-height:20px;font-family:inherit;text-align:left;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mjjtniro-riz192\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(0, 209, 0);font-size:18px;\">#02</span></a></span></strong></span><strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;最省心：阶跃 AI 桌面助手</span></strong></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2em;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px 10px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">我目前在高频使用如下两个功能：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2em;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px 10px 16px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.每天早上定时自动拆解一个 Github 上的热门 AI 开源项目</span><span leaf=\"\"> \n      <br> \n     </span><span leaf=\"\">2.记录我全天的工作内容</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于第一个功能，是我之前分享过的那个拆解开源项目的“定时自动化”版本。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006826\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=10d76101&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJa7ZttafqXeJLnZ9Z8RhR4zx3ZQZ5b2niatibWpMFu4jNbiaPicgtbpfxAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D4\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面是任务的要求（需要右滑）：</span></p>\n    <pre style=\"border-radius:8px;box-shadow:inset 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);padding:0 !important;margin:10px 8px;font-size:90%;overflow-x:auto;line-height:1.5;\"><code data-language-pending=\"\" data-raw-code=\"打开 Github trending（地址：\" star=\"star\" ai=\"ai\" clone=\"clone\" your=\"your\" lt=\"lt\" data-show-line-number=\"false\" style=\"\"><span leaf=\"\">打开 Github trending（地址：`<a href=\"https://github.com/trending`），查看每一个热门项目的介绍，选择一个\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/trending`），查看每一个热门项目的介绍，选择一个</a> Star 最多的大模型、AI 相关的项目，把它 Clone 到本地`/YOUR/PATH/TO/codes/githubtrending`路径下（Clone 前检查路径下是否已有项目，已有就换一个），按照下面的方法对项目进行大模型应用拆解：</span><p><span leaf=\"\"><br></span></p><span leaf=\"\">&lt;howPrompt的提示词&gt;</span></code></pre>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后它就会每天 9:00 雷打不动的打开 Github 热榜、找到 AI 相关的项目、随机挑一个、下载到本地、按</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">howPromt</span></code><span leaf=\"\">提示词的约束拆解分析、输出一份报告。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006832\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6453703703703704\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=287ec31a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJROFbldS0UTUVkAahMib1B76HQLx7ibuRMKLF0DicMkrXDh3iaAyel4iaiaoA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D5\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">howPrompt</span></code><span leaf=\"\">的提示词我最近又更新了一版，增加了功能实现(时序图)和工具 tools 使用两个板块。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">新的提示词也同步更新在 AI 学习圈圈友空间了，感兴趣或者已经在用的小伙伴可以更新一下。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006834\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.49722222222222223\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=93242d9f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJY30MhJ0DmbXaDKJ2Isjo8zjBNGbjTERpzHl9flLwiae8VQSabspNkFg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D6\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二个是工具最近刚刚更新的能力，叫做</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">全局记忆</span></code><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">它会每隔 5s 截取我当前电脑活动的界面，发送给模型识别分析，生成一段行为摘要。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006833\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=fd126b2c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJXZP46y3624Lgibib5WPVlmP4teq1PwolecZfXGAaqLw12U32dYu4Awtg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D7\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">每天 20:00 它会根据当前记录的内容，生成一份全天的总结。包括我各个应用上的使用时长、工作内容、分钟级时间线等等。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006831\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6666666666666666\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertica