-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">以及，你可以在群里讨论任何与 AI 相关的工具、应用问题，几乎都能找到答案。</span></p>\n    <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100006836\" alt=\"图片\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5074074074074074\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: block;margin: 0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;vertical-align: baseline;height: auto !important;visibility: visible !important;width: 100%;box-sizing:border-box;max-width:100% !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=63d3b40e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FtQO69fPQdGhEl3FbgbbhG7VXK33IqUfJ93x0XMGBX1BGkBrjqNh8DxxKJYVDSqNicia9uicWRzKsVu6ZeKYkKBgjg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D13\"></span>\n     <figcaption style=\"text-align: center;color: #888;font-size: 0.8em;\"></figcaption>\n    </figure>\n    <h3 data-heading=\"true\" style=\"margin:2em 8px 0.75em 0;border-left:4px solid #333333;padding-left:12px;font-size:17px;line-height:1.2;border-bottom:1px dashed #333333;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">腾讯文档-圈友空间</span></strong></h3>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">用来沉淀体系化、深度的 AI 文章和超长的工程化提示词，不定期更新。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align:left;line-height: 2;font-size: 15px;margin: 10px;letter-spacing: 0.1em;color: #646a73;font-weight: normal;min-height: 20px;visibility: visible;font-family:inherit;\"><span leaf=\"\">当前包括：</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27, 31, 35, 0.05);padding: 3px 5px;border-radius: 4px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Claude code</span></code><span leaf=\"\">、</span><code style=\"font-size: 90%;color: #d14;background: rgba(27,